285
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:42,800
<i>...you won't let your efforts go to waste.</i>

286
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:46,520
<i>Su Zaizai,</i>

287
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:48,920
<i>the mimosa flowers are about to bloom.</i>

